channel.title: Webclient refuses to unpack the cache
channel.description:
I created a 317 Webclient and uploaded the Cache to fileden.
The Webclient downloads the cache completely but afterwards it says "unpacking files" and then says "Reload client" and it deletes the cache.
How would I get my webclient to correctly unpack the cache?

item.title: Webclient refuses to unpack the cache
item.dc:creator: @I_Yaa_I I Yaa I
item.description:
@I_Yaa_I wrote:

If you are the owner of the webclient then i suggest that you put your cache for download on uppit or something. Then all they have to do is download it and extract it and put it in local disc c.
